(1, 'Coco', '', '2017-10-27', 109, 7.6, 'Despite his familyâ€™s baffling generations-old ban on music, Miguel dreams of becoming an accomplished musician like his idol, Ernesto de la Cruz. Desperate to prove his talent, Miguel finds himself in the stunning and colorful Land of the Dead following a mysterious chain of events. Along the way, he meets charming trickster Hector, and together, they set off on an extraordinary journey to unlock the real story behind Miguel''s family history.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/eKi8dIrr8voobbaGzDpe8w0PVbC.jpg', 354912),
(2, 'Star Wars: The Last Jedi', '', '2017-12-13', 152, 7.5, 'Rey develops her newly discovered abilities with the guidance of Luke Skywalker, who is unsettled by the strength of her powers. Meanwhile, the Resistance prepares to do battle with the First Order.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/xGWVjewoXnJhvxKW619cMzppJDQ.jpg', 181808),
(3, 'Daddy''s Home 2', '', '2017-11-09', 100, 5.6, 'Brad and Dusty must deal with their intrusive fathers during the holidays.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/rF2IoKL0IFmumEXQFUuB8LajTYP.jpg', 419680),
(4, 'Justice League', '', '2017-11-15', 120, 6.6, 'Fueled by his restored faith in humanity and inspired by Superman''s selfless act, Bruce Wayne and Diana Prince assemble a team of metahumans consisting of Barry Allen, Arthur Curry, and Victor Stone to face the catastrophic threat of Steppenwolf and the Parademons who are on the hunt for three Mother Boxes on Earth.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/9rtrRGeRnL0JKtu9IMBWsmlmmZz.jpg', 141052),
(5, 'Murder on the Orient Express', '', '2017-11-03', 114, 6.8, 'Genius Belgian detective Hercule Poirot investigates the murder of an American tycoon aboard the Orient Express train.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/iBlfxlw8qwtUS0R8YjIU7JtM6LM.jpg', 392044),
(6, 'The Star', '', '2017-11-15', 86, 4.5, 'A small but brave donkey and his animal friends become the unsung heroes of the greatest story ever told, the first Christmas.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/tEbDvivUfsCupngKIfMJJ725eAD.jpg', 355547),
(7, 'Thor: Ragnarok', '', '2017-10-25', 130, 7.5, 'Thor is imprisoned on the other side of the universe and finds himself in a race against time to get back to Asgard to stop Ragnarok, the prophecy of destruction to his homeworld and the end of Asgardian civilization, at the hands of an all-powerful new threat, the ruthless Hela.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/oSLd5GYGsiGgzDPKTwQh7wamO8t.jpg', 284053),
(8, 'The Disaster Artist', '', '2017-12-01', 103, 7.4, 'An aspiring actor in Hollywood meets an enigmatic stranger by the name of Tommy Wiseau, the meeting leads the actor down a path nobody could have predicted; creating the worst movie ever made.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/jj84nF5vYRD0HUTowBKcrKk8hZP.jpg', 371638),
(9, 'Happy Death Day', '', '2017-10-12', 96, 6.3, 'A college student relives the day of her murder over and over again as she tries to discover her killer''s identity.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/cTaEIUYTt52ooq9quVbAQ7NpGwo.jpg', 440021),
(10, 'Roman J. Israel, Esq.', '', '2017-11-10', 129, 5.5, 'Hard-nosed liberal lawyer Roman J. Israel has been fighting the good fight forever while others take the credit. When his partner, the firmâ€™s frontman, has a heart attack, Israel suddenly takes on that role. He soon discovers some unsettling truths about the firm--truths that conflict with his values of helping the poor and dispossessed--and finds himself in an existential crisis that leads to extreme actions.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/8e5IGlLrVjwrlDcRtzSQkXhJFWl.jpg', 413362),
(11, 'Wonder', '', '2017-11-13', 113, 7.6, 'Based on the New York Times bestseller, Wonder tells the inspiring and heartwarming story of August Pullman. Born with facial differences that, up until now, have prevented him from going to a mainstream school, Auggie becomes the most unlikely of heroes when he enters the local fifth grade. As his family, his new classmates, and the larger community all struggle to find their compassion and acceptance, Auggie''s extraordinary journey will unite them all and prove you can''t blend in when you were born to stand out.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/ouYgAatYH4JzIThj6FI3UYf31RI.jpg', 406997),
(12, 'Olaf''s Frozen Adventure', '', '2017-10-27', 23, 6.7, 'Olaf is on a mission to harness the best holiday traditions for Anna, Elsa, and Kristoff.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/47pLZ1gr63WaciDfHCpmoiXJlVr.jpg', 460793),
(13, 'The Shape of Water', '', '2017-12-01', 123, 6.9, 'An other-worldly story, set against the backdrop of Cold War era America circa 1962, where a mute janitor working at a lab falls in love with an amphibious man being held captive there and devises a plan to help him escape.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/iLYLADGA5oKGM92Ns1j9CDgk3iI.jpg', 399055),
(14, 'The Tribes of Palos Verdes', '', '2017-12-01', 104, 6.1, 'When the situation at her idyllic Palos Verdes home turns volatile, young Medina attempts to surf her way to happiness.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/8w4JecmVtqcSMk4mdiHURzISsYz.jpg', 324562),
(15, 'Darkest Hour', '', '2017-11-22', 114, 3.6, 'A thrilling and inspiring true story begins on the eve of World War II as, within days of becoming Prime Minister of Great Britain, Winston Churchill must face one of his most turbulent and defining trials: exploring a negotiated peace treaty with Nazi Germany, or standing firm to fight for the ideals, liberty and freedom of a nation. As the unstoppable Nazi forces roll across Western Europe and the threat of invasion is imminent, and with an unprepared public, a skeptical King, and his own party plotting against him, Churchill must withstand his darkest hour, rally a nation, and attempt to change the course of world history.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/67fPL6ZaiOeM4hYqpxqV9Py8psJ.jpg', 399404),
(16, 'Jumanji: Welcome to the Jungle', '', '2017-12-08', 119, 5.7, 'The tables are turned as four teenagers are sucked into Jumanji''s world - pitted against rhinos, black mambas and an endless variety of jungle traps and puzzles. To survive, they''ll play as characters from the game.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/bXrZ5iHBEjH7WMidbUDQ0U2xbmr.jpg', 353486),
(17, 'Bullet Head', '', '2017-12-07', 140, 4.5, 'A group of career criminals finds itself trapped in a warehouse with the law â€“ and an Attack Dog named DeNiro closing in.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/ySmKQPjWnNzuZ5YliQaOVEnWn2.jpg', 480572),
(18, 'Wonder Wheel', '', '2017-12-01', 101, 4.8, 'The story of four characters whose lives intertwine amid the hustle and bustle of the Coney Island amusement park in the 1950s: Ginny, an emotionally volatile former actress now working as a waitress in a clam house; Humpty, Ginnyâ€™s rough-hewn carousel operator husband; Mickey, a handsome young lifeguard who dreams of becoming a playwright; and Carolina, Humptyâ€™s long-estranged daughter, who is now hiding out from gangsters at her fatherâ€™s apartment.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/fPXn8SW4pa4kJErAIAJLmb3Znns.jpg', 429189),
(19, 'The Man Who Invented Christmas', '', '2017-11-22', 104, 4.2, 'After a series his books have been flops, Charles Dickens decides to write and self-publish A Christmas Carol.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/qRkzRue5rTzB6PESXBJCKqROOXC.jpg', 450322),
(20, 'November Criminals', '', '2017-12-08', 85, 4.3, 'Addison Schacht investigates the murder of his friend Kevin, with the help of Pheobe, and they discover the truth is darker than they ever imagined.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/m2JxGgarPvtemudLZ1CB6gLJeUb.jpg', 317091),
(21, 'Paddington 2', '', '2017-11-10', 103, 8, 'Paddington, now happily settled with the Brown family and a popular member of the local community, picks up a series of odd jobs to buy the perfect present for his Aunt Lucy''s 100th birthday, only for the gift to be stolen.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/bU5pSpQfXRmqDd6jthmP8iWJOjd.jpg', 346648),
(22, 'A Family for the Holidays', '', '2017-12-01', 90, 2.8, 'When family conflicts arise between happy couple Hallie and Lucas on the week before their big day, their plans for a breezy wedding in the tropics take a turn and their love is tested when they are forced to put on a small town winter wedding in the snow.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/5AEF0M6yhVUQ4fq967jfDXbA3mk.jpg', 480919),
(23, 'Home Again', '', '2017-09-07', 97, 5.3, 'Life for a single mom in Los Angeles takes an unexpected turn when she allows three young guys to move in with her.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/pE4VHzhDZgvbx2QOllaXXPADiW1.jpg', 427900),
(24, 'Love Beats Rhymes', '', '2017-12-01', 105, 5.5, 'An aspiring hip-hop artist discovers the world of slam poetry.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/40DTqW72Igok7ilNJ5ju6HWYhpi.jpg', 376658),
(25, 'å¥‡é–€é��ç”²', '', '2017-12-15', 0, 0, 'The world is on the brink of catastrophe in a chaotic age where evil demons roam. In order to keep evil at bay, a mysterious organisation from the pugilist world emerges. A new constable and a young girl with a mysterious past are also drawn into this group, and the group embarks on an incredible adventure.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/9xNPbMPXJfjxPvu70MQtbp9jI6i.jpg', 460557),
