(30, 'The Party', '', '2017-09-13', 71, 6.7, 'Various individuals think theyâ€™re coming together for a party in a private homer, but a series of revelations results in a huge crisis that throws their belief systems â€“ and their values into total disarray.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/rzpbqnmMBtoNKwqwbp2KMaZmwWw.jpg', 415401),
(31, 'Soufra', '', '2017-12-15', 73, 0, 'The unlikely and wildly inspirational story of intrepid social entrepreneur, Mariam Shaar â€“ a generational refugee who has spent her entire life in the Burj El Barajneh refugee camp just south of Beirut, Lebanon. Follow Mariam as she sets out against all odds to change her fate by launching a successful catering company, â€œSoufra,â€� and then expand it into a food truck business with a diverse team of fellow refugee woman who now share this camp as their home.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/zZguaI0gQZQlTDr7FJapFKZVZLE.jpg', 483827),
(32, 'å�›ã�®è†µè‡“ã‚’ã�Ÿã�¹ã�Ÿã�„', '', '2017-07-28', 115, 4.8, 'I (Takumi Kitamura) am a high school student. I happen to find a diary by my classmate Sakura Yamauchi (Minami Hamabe) that reveals she is suffering from a pancreatic disease. I spent time with Sakura, but she dies.  12 years later, due to Sakuraâ€™s words, I (Shun Oguri) am now a high school teacher at the same school where I graduated from. While I talk with my student, I remember several months I spent with Sakura. Meanwhile, Kyoko (Keiko Kitagawa), who was Sakuraâ€™s friend, is soon to marry. Kyoko also recalls the days she spent with me and Sakura.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/zM8Gzl1g0ndINg0qbSIHXnKgVci.jpg', 449132),
(33, 'Santa & Cie', '', '2017-12-06', 99, 6, 'Christmas is on it''s way and with it disaster. The 92,000 responsible for manufacturing children''s toys all become sick at the same time! It''s a tough moment for Santa, better known as Father Christmas. He''s left no choice: he must make an emergency trip to Earth with his reindeer to search for a remedy. When he arrives, he must find some allies to save the magic of Christmas.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/zfFgIQFtwAR8FxbMHB9eEZr9GhO.jpg', 451500),
