(36, 'Christmas Lights', '', '2017-12-20', 5, 0, 'Jake gets home from work on a December night, and ponders about how screwed up the world is and why Christmas is the most wonderful time of the year.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/rwNhXtDc2fCUdL899VJnLtgbr5E.jpg', 490416),
(37, 'HAGER', '', '2017-12-15', 85, 0, 'After his colleague Schweitzer goes missing during a drug raid, undercover cop Till Hager is tasked with tracking down a mysterious new drug called "Abaddon" - a substance which supposedly drags it''s users down the deepest depths of hell.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2null', 460290),
(38, 'The Limehouse Golem', '', '2016-12-23', 109, 6, 'A series of murders has shaken the community to the point where people believe that only a legendary creature from dark times â€“ the mythical Golem â€“ must be responsible.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/wvc4t0Hs31ChgIhHzvw49kGejXj.jpg', 369300),
(39, 'The Florida Project', '', '2017-10-07', 115, 7.9, 'The story of a precocious six year-old and her ragtag group of friends whose summer break is filled with childhood wonder, possibility and a sense of adventure while the adults around them struggle with hard times.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/bnSTP1PY2fDyat0eUa4QouuGV7F.jpg', 394117),
(40, 'Perfectos desconocidos', '', '2017-12-01', 0, 7.6, 'The story unfolds over the course of one night, during a lunar eclipse, in the home of Alfonso and Evaâ€”a well-healed professional couple worried about their teenage daughter and about the monotony of their lives. They are joined by five guests: Eduardo and Blanco, Antonio and Ana and Pepe. Itâ€™s a dinner party like any other, until someone has an intriguing idea: what if they put their mobile phones at the disposition of the group, leaving them in the middle of the table for everyone to see?', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/8wAFD7rtdYEnJEblDFeyjbKoazS.jpg', 435126),
(41, 'La corrispondenza', '', '2016-01-14', 116, 6.2, 'The relationship between Ed, a married astronomer and Amy, his lover, who spend their years apart, is based only on phone calls and texts. One day Amy begins noticing something strange in Ed''s messages.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/ghuK137xSNdtZWxXqG96GUFLeYR.jpg', 315880),
(42, 'Le sens de la fÃªte', '', '2017-10-04', 115, 7.1, 'Max is a battle-weary veteran of the wedding-planning racket. His latest â€” and last â€” gig is a hell of a fÃªte, involving stuffy period costumes for the caterers, a vain, hyper- sensitive singer who thinks he''s a Gallic James Brown, and a morose, micromanaging groom determined to make Max''s night as miserable as possible. But what makes the affair too bitter to endure is that Max''s colleague and ostensible girlfriend, Joisette, seems to have written him off, coolly going about her professional duties while openly flirting with a much younger server. It''s going to be a very long nightâ€¦ especially once the groom''s aerial serenade gets underway.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/e71GmI2Ki9JwnGgMKJTDnlMFS71.jpg', 432068),
(43, 'Battle of the Sexes', '', '2017-09-22', 121, 7.3, 'The true story of the 1973 tennis match between World number one Billie Jean King and ex-champ and serial hustler Bobby Riggs.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/v3y96NrwyBxqNhVpHIBZix0uPKP.jpg', 369192),
(44, 'Tiger Zinda Hai', '', '2017-12-22', 0, 0, 'RAW agent Tiger/Avinash Singh Rathore returns from the dead to take on an international terrorist organisation but this time he has his wife Zoya by his side.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/6EHnmwCtBhfOuoKQaHUSACV5UUJ.jpg', 441909),
(45, 'The Promise', '', '2016-12-02', 130, 7.1, 'Set during the last days of the Ottoman Empire, a love triangle develops between Mikael, a brilliant medical student, the beautiful and sophisticated artist Ana, and Chris, a renowned American journalist based in Paris.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/iDWer2VFikupdqDc7d5sxCWZ3gW.jpg', 354859),
(46, 'Monsoon Shootout', '', '2017-12-15', 88, 0, 'Amit Kumar''s debut feature is a taut thriller exploring police violence, corruption and the moral quandary facing an idealistic rookie cop. Depicting an India in which extrajudicial murders by the police are commonplace, Kumar takes one of these ''encounters'' as the starting point for a compact and riveting ride through Mumbai''s underworld.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/gzBdH7LawD5ma2IPuGJ2M9zd1Ic.jpg', 194522),
(47, 'Mysterious Skin', '', '2004-05-20', 105, 7.4, 'A teenage hustler and a young man obsessed with alien abductions cross paths, together discovering a horrible, liberating truth.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/wynnf6LT4ueuCuREPRMtHGQIk5T.jpg', 11171),
(48, 'Pengabdi Setan', '', '2017-09-28', 107, 7.4, 'After Rini''s mother died, something is disturbing her family.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/2XB9EO9L8t0ryipAoB9WlsxXOIl.jpg', 467012),
(49, 'Vuil Wasgoed', '', '2017-12-22', 100, 0, 'Wim and Kevin work at a laundromat. By day, things are boring, but when the sun sets they party in their clientsâ€™ clothes. During a party, they discover a chopped-off finger in a clientâ€™s suitâ€™s jacket. The underhanded owner of the finger, his sons, and a ruthless traitor are hot on Wim and Kevinâ€™s heels and have no regard for their safety.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/jmH5ycwtFadb2Kq71gfZxYHPEmx.jpg', 467180),
(50, 'Bleeding Steel', '', '2017-12-22', 0, 0, 'Jackie Chan stars as a hardened special forces agent who fights to protect a young woman from a sinister criminal gang. At the same time he with feels a special connection to the young woman, like they met in a different life.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/z1O26qVwkhSlicycBBK731k8vPd.jpg', 460648),
(51, 'é‹¼ã�®éŒ¬é‡‘è¡“å¸«', '', '2017-12-14', 0, 0, 'Two alchemist brothers go on a quest for the Philosopher''s Stone after an attempt to revive their dead mother goes horribly wrong.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/h5Vjeamp47cMjsaX1mklMyTC3TO.jpg', 426285),
(52, 'Atomic Blonde', '', '2017-07-26', 115, 6, 'An undercover MI6 agent is sent to Berlin during the Cold War to investigate the murder of a fellow agent and recover a missing list of double agents.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/kV9R5h0Yct1kR8Hf8sJ1nX0Vz4x.jpg', 341013),
(53, 'Garde alternÃ©e', '', '2017-12-20', 0, 0, 'No thing!', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/heGJlmfQUn7rqNsBUF04Jv3v8sw.jpg', 451504),
