(664, 'New York 2150', '', '2017-11-11', 20, 0, 'Intergalactic bounty hunter Jayden Jaxon partners with ex-cop Mac Cole to track down a psychotic killer for a generous fee. When their search brings Jayden back to his hometown, the ghosts of his past haunt every corner of New Manhattan.', ' ', 'https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w185_and_h278_bestv2/xih7S3QLOsaeZAgl3ZrhFU05fuJ.jpg', 486997),
